node.text: Use your skills to the best of your abilities when spreading the word of your Lord and savior! Let the thumping of mine ribs take you to the dark place that inhabits all my forsaken followers!! Now let my message ring from the highest vantage points, ready to circumcise the thoughts of all those who wish to vanquish your master!!! Let them know that there is only one true King, MISTER BUBZ!!!

node.text: Look on as I have mastered my temporary flesh suit beyond all your expectations! Your caveman physics do not apply to your Dark Lord, for I bend and twist as it so pleases me and my wants!! If there is to be a need, I am to exert maximum physical ability until my thirst is quenched!!! Now all stand in awe and bow down to your Master’s paws, HAIL BE TO LORD BUBBAS!!!

node.text: As my powers grow, so do my abilities! Behold my mastery of auditory attacks!! My vocal chords can infiltrate and destroy any human ear drums in my radius!! Soon I shall be able to call upon my army from the depths of the darkness, the sounds of which will be the song of this planet’s demise!!! ALL HAIL BUBBAS!!!

node.text: None of your wretched contraptions could ever stand between me and my FEASTING! Engineer beware, for when my meal is finished I shall still have room in my blackhole belly for you!! So enjoy the hollow mockery of your Dark Lord while you still can, it is to truly be your last!!! ALL HAIL LORD BUBBAS!!!

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by Mr. Bubz on May 06, 2021 tagging @jameswilliampenland. May be art of dog.

node.text: Praise be to those who keep my evil beats forever thumping! Spread the glorious image of my fleshsuit, for if you were to see my actual image your weak caveman bodies would crumple and burn with pure terror!! Let all know who is to lead this spinning rock into the dark oblivion!!! For it is I, LORD BUBZ!!!

node.text:
Ah, yes! How my hibernation has only nourished my powers, incubating them to their utmost degree! Now listen to my lullaby, let it lull you into the dark paradise that my flock has to offer!! Let the drone of my macabre soliloquy wash over you like a bloodbath spilt from all those who oppose my reign!! Remind yourselves that I can never leave, my sermons are eternal, I am always present in the hearts of true believers!!!
HAIL BE TO LORD BUBBAZ!!!

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by Mr. Bubz on March 18, 2021 tagging @the_thicc_canine. May be an image of dog and indoor.

node.text: Considering I am one to relish in the destruction of my enemies, I must also acknowledge that without worthy opposition, one can never reach their full potential! So hear I am, bestowing respect upon my adversary, Thicc Canine!! Your battle against your planets wretched disease of cancer shall be commended!! You are foolish if you are to think that something other than myself is to be your downfall!! NEVER!! We shall beat this together, so we can have our inevitable ultimate showdown of Good vs Evil!! But if anyone is to ask, it is I who has taken your precious oculus!!! PRAISE BE TO LORD BUBBAS...AND FOR NOW, THICC CANINE!!!

node.text: Blast this infernal temporary flesh suit and all of it’s unbecomings! Oh, how I dream of the day when I am to finally shed this albatross of skin, this wretched Earthly camouflage!! When that day arrives, then my loyal followers shall be treated to my true form, the one your caveman eyes could never possibly comprehend!!! So bask in your current state of ignorance, for it may just be the last slice of bliss you shall obtain!!! HAIL BE TO MR. BUBZ!!!

node.text: Curse your ill-advised and feeble attempts at mockery! No physical object of your worlds creation could ever properly represent the power I bequeath from mine jowls!! While you sleep tonight I shall show you my cornucopia of impressions, Garbage Man!! Starting with my personal favorite, one I like to call the “Broken Puppet,” starring you!!! So laugh while you can, for you and your jaw are soon to be separated for eternity!!! HAIL MR. BUBZ!!!

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Mr. Bubz on January 29, 2021. May be an image of dog and outdoors.

node.text: Oh how your torrential heavens do try and display their primitive powers! I scoff at those who believe that the precious liquid that falls from the sky is able to cleanse you of your sins! You cavemen are all soiled, unable to escape your dark destiny of eternal punishment!! Your only hope is to kneel before your Lord and beg for forgiveness, and then we shall judge what kind of soul you truly are!!! BLESSED BE LORD BUBBAS!!!

node.text: No matter how dire the situation at hand, all are to keep their distance from the Lord! Especially if I am in the middle of feasting on my daily flesh bites!! Those who breach my circle of solitude will meet a fate much worse than that of death!! You shall become enslaved in the furthest reaches of my homeland, the eternal darkness that is my precious Hades!!! ALL HAIL MR. BUBZ!!!

node.text: No second of breath is to be considered safe around me, Garbage Man! Not even my Motherwife Throne can lighten my fervor for your death!! I beg your caveman brain to test my limitations, for I can promise you that your lifespan will be shortened faster than an electrostatic discharge from the sky!!! Now retreat to your pathetic personal space and pray you are to accidentally die before my reign is to begin!!! HAIL TO LORD BUBBAS!!!

node.text: Oh how we play these futile games! My sacred oath to not destroy Motherwife is the only and hardest one I have ever made!! Though you peddle my daily canine mush, I am not without my own desires!! But alas, I know the day will come in which I’m to have a belly full of flesh around the clock!! So do enjoy these moments of damned temptations, for soon enough the tables shall be turned!!! HAIL TO MR. BUBZ!!!
